headline: Healthpeak Properties Announces Tax Treatment of 2024 Distributions
summary: DENVER, January 15, 2025--Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC), a leading owner, operator, and developer of real estate for healthcare discovery and delivery, announced today the tax treatment of its 2024 distributions.
